des: The feed reads "strategies" developed by Brian Eno and Peter Schmidt. Each strategy offers a challenging constraint intended to help artists (particularly musicians) break creative blocks by encouraging lateral thinking. These strategies are sure to help you in unlocking new creative ways to solve problems and create solutions.
